About This Application

Project Overview

This is a modern full-stack web application built with React and Node.js/Express. It demonstrates best practices for building scalable web applications with a clean separation between frontend and backend concerns.

Technology Stack

React 18

Modern UI library with hooks and functional components

Node.js

JavaScript runtime for server-side development

Express.js

Fast, unopinionated web framework for Node.js

SCSS

CSS preprocessor for enhanced styling capabilities

Axios

Promise-based HTTP client for API requests

React Router

Declarative routing for React applications

Features

  • Responsive design that works on all devices
  • Modern React patterns with hooks and functional components
  • RESTful API with proper error handling
  • Real-time server health monitoring
  • User management with CRUD operations
  • Beautiful UI with glassmorphism design
  • Production-ready configuration

Getting Started

  1. Install dependencies: npm install
  2. Install client dependencies: npm run install-client
  3. Start development server: npm run dev
  4. Open your browser to http://localhost:3000
